                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I've checked some other vodka sauce recipes and most call for 3/4 to 1 cup of Vodka <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" />    Most of the vodka "flavor" will cook out, however if you're worried that it will be too strong, start with 3/4 cup
