                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Vodka Sauce and Pasta /blink
<br />

<br />
Forget about the Sauce, get her to drink loads of Vodka and it won't matter how badly the Pasta turns out  <img src="images/smiles/icon_exclaim.gif" alt="icon_exclaim.gif" border="0" /> 
<br />

<br />
Depending on what you are after there are loads of different recipies you can use. Basically, the more vodka you use the more dilute the sauce and stronger tasting (of vodka). To counter this you need more ingreadiants... If you bring the sauce above about 67c then the alchol will just boil off.
<br />

<br />
Best bet is to select 4-5 of them that you reckon are easy and spend the next week practicing.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
