                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Very easy vodka sauce recipe:
<br />

<br />
Can of crushed tomatoes
<br />
Fresh garlic
<br />
Crushed red pepper flakes
<br />

<br />
Simmer together in pan
<br />

<br />
Add vodka
<br />

<br />
Simmer more
<br />

<br />
Add heavy cream if you want a "pink" sauce
<br />

<br />
Everything is done to taste.  Experiment a bit.  They're cheap igredients.  I don't add cheese to the sauce because I prefer to have grated parmesan and a sprig of fresh basil topping the completed dish.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
                </table></td>
        </tr>
